'''Ano Panta''' (el: Άνω Πάντα) is one of the two regions of [[Othoni]] island, near [[Corfu]], [[Greece]]. It includes the western villages of the island (Chorio, Dafni, Stavros etc.) while '''Kato Panta''' (el: Κάτω Πάντα) covers the central and eastern part of Othoni.<ref name=akron>{{cite book|title=Ιόνιον άκρων, εκδόσεις |publisher=ΈΨΙΛΟΝ |year=2000 |isbn=960-7062-99-X}}</ref>{{rp|37}}<ref>http://www.topontiki.gr/article/249880/othonoi-nisi-tis-kalypsoys-einai-dytikotero-simeio-tis-elladas-photos-video</ref>
