'''Morgoth''' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ɔːr|ɡ|ɒ|θ}} is a small dark region on the surface of [[Pluto]], southwest of the [[Norgay Montes]] and adjacent to [[Quidlivun Cavus]]. The ''[[New Horizons]]'' spacecraft discovered it in 2015 and named it [[Morgoth]], the primary antagonist in the mythology of J.R.R. Tolkien.
